---
title: Turkey Feta Patties with Bulgur Greek Salad & Creamy Lemon Dill Sauce
description: Sometimes you want a patty without the bread, which is why our chefs came up with this turkey patty and grain meal for you. Ground turkey mingles with tangy feta, crisp scallion, garlic, and a mix of sauces and spices. The patties are shallow-fried, then drizzled with a creamy lemon dill sauce. It’s all served on top of a Greek-style grain salad that features nutty bulgur, fresh cucumber, tomato, and dill, plus a squeeze of tart lemon juice. Trust us: you’ll gobble this meal right up.
